Author: ZODIAQ
Title: [ANN][ICO][ZOD] ZODIAQ | Crypto-fiat blockchain platform. MVP.
Body: We have new important advisers, such as Valery Petrov (https://twitter.com/zodiaq_io). A personal account in our bank has been developed (https://sso.z.cryptobank.team/) the site of our stock exchange has been launched (http://zodiaq.naxdev.com/#/)  Quote from: yuliteva on May 14, 2018, 07:41:09 AM do you plan to make a hedge fund ?  Yes we do.  Quote from: Costa_one on May 14, 2018, 08:53:04 AM how can I fill in my account ?  A personal account in our bank has been developed https://sso.z.cryptobank.team/ it works in test mode.   When I can sold my tokens ? Tokens purchased in the first round can be sold after the end of the second round.  Project Tokens can be purchased only for btc and ETH or for fiat, too, is possible? On the pre-ICO only for the BTC and the ETH, on the ICO we will sort out the possibility of receiving the fiat, the solution will be announced later.  What are the opportunities for the employees? The recruitment campaign will be announced and launched upon completion of the ICO.  What happens in case participants have not enough funds to complete the transaction? Do you mean the participants of the ICO?  You want to offer platform for exchange fiat to crypto and conversely? Yes, this is one of the main functions, but there are much more.   Something like Localbitcoin but for more currencies? Rather like Coinbase.  In what case the transaction can be executed automatically? What transaction is meant?  What is the essence of Zodiaq bank ? This is one of the first banks in the world that received a banking license for operations with both fiat and crypto-currencies. Also unlike most crypto banks, already has a developed software platform, connection to SWIFT and FATCA GIIN. That is almost ready to launch.

Title: [ANN][ICO][ZOD] ZODIAQ | Crypto-fiat blockchain platform. MVP.
Body: Quote from: butt786 on April 27, 2018, 09:30:03 PM Very interesting, Thx u  for your Remark, Need More Detailed Data About The Participants Will Be Later. As Soon  Zodiaq strategic aim is formation of new financial infrastructure, which will replace classical banks as a managing service for implementation of transactions between contraparties.  Due to the widely developed infrastructure of relationships with a large number of financial services and the formation of its own foreign exchange reserves, post-trade processing consumer services will be launched within core business units of Zodiaq system. This mechanism will allow instant cashless transfers in the local currency ZOD for counter obligations between users and companies for sold and delivered goods, financial instruments and services performed, based on clearings within the ecosystem contour.
